<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/adventuretime.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <nav>
        <h1>Quiz</h1>
        <a href="/">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-house-icon lucide-house"><path d="M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8"/><path d="M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-6a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 6A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
            <p>Home</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/quiz">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clipboard-pen-icon lucide-clipboard-pen"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"/><path d="M21.34 15.664a1 1 0 1 0-3.004-3.004l-5.01 5.012a2 2 0 0 0-.506.854l-.837 2.87a.5.5 0 0 0 .62.62l2.87-.837a2 2 0 0 0 .854-.506z"/><path d="M8 22H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1"/></svg>
            <p>Quiz</p>
        </a>
        <a href="">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-store-icon lucide-store"><path d="M15 21v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v5"/><path d="M17.774 10.31a1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.451 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.548 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.452 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.77-3.248l2.889-4.184A2 2 0 0 1 7 2h10a2 2 0 0 1 1.653.873l2.895 4.192a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.774 3.244"/><path d="M4 10.95V19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8.05"/></svg>
            <p>Shop</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/about">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-info-icon lucide-info"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
            <p>About</p>
        </a>
        <div class="more">
            <div class="more-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-ellipsis-icon lucide-ellipsis"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="19" cy="12" r="1"/><circle cx="5" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p>More</p>
            <div></div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Home</h1>
      <p>
        This application uses the Open Trivia Database (OpenTDB) to load trivia
        questions dynamically through a backend proxy.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Frontend fetches: <code>/api/quiz/questions</code></li>
        <li>
          Backend controller uses OpenTDB API:
          <code>https://opentdb.com/api.php</code>
        </li>
        <li>Results are displayed on the quiz interface</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Get started by taking a quiz on the <a href="/quiz">quiz</a> page.</p>
      <p>
        Learn more about this Express app on the
        <a href="/about">About</a> page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
